init_text: When you're 28, science discovers a drug that stops all effects of aging, creating immortality. Your government decides to give the drug to all citizens under 26, but you and the rest of the "Lost Generations" are deemed too high-risk. When you're 85, the side effects are finally discovered.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: In other words, over the course of a century, you will reach a maximum state of happiness equivalent to that of the most miserable person on earth.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You go to a suicide clinic and sign up for the "suicide tour" - a 90-day, round-the-world trip with other

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Your tour guide is a man with a terminal case of the "Sads", who finds new and creative ways to add to your unhappiness.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: There is a parody of the film "The Wizard of Oz" called "The Wizard of Sads".
